{"id":643763,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【敏感词库】dada与锦拼/","date":"2020-05-11T07:11:46Z","modified":"2020-05-11T07:17:56Z","title":"【敏感词库】“dada”与“锦拼”","content":"<p>5月11日，有推友发起“敏感词测试”活动，称有两段文字在豆瓣说因触及“敏感词”而无法直接发出，受到内容的后续人工审核，希望大家可以“看图找词”。多名网友表示“题目太难”，难以找出所涉敏感词。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">敏感词测试时间！请找出敏感词： <a href=\"https://t.co/mPd2gD67qM\">pic.twitter.com/mPd2gD67qM</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 卡樂BB😘🏴🇹🇼🏳️‍🌈🇲🇳 (@wqicui) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wqicui/status/1259502720286814208?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643766\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqnC6cU0AEay-4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"471\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqnC6cU0AEay-4.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqnC6cU0AEay-4-287x300.jpeg 287w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqnC6cU0AEay-4-979x1024.jpeg 979w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqnC6cU0AEay-4-768x804.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643767\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqvi7FU8AA35eZ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"754\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqvi7FU8AA35eZ.jpeg 543w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXqvi7FU8AA35eZ-159x300.jpeg 159w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>而最终答案被揭晓后，大家才得知，所涉敏感词均与<strong>习近平</strong>有关。</p>\n<p>其中第一张图，“A whole new worl<strong>d。A da</strong>zzling place I never knew。”触及到“dada”（大大）的拼音，甚至dada还被句号所隔开。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643768\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXquKR6UMAEGbSb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXquKR6UMAEGbSb.jpeg 1125w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXquKR6UMAEGbSb-300x272.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXquKR6UMAEGbSb-1024x929.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXquKR6UMAEGbSb-768x697.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXquKR6UMAEGbSb-1080x980.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>第二张图，则是“香肠杂<strong>锦拼</strong>盘”的“锦拼”与“近平”的拼音相似。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643771\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXtLZL1UMAE_yNu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"927\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXtLZL1UMAE_yNu.jpeg 994w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXtLZL1UMAE_yNu-146x300.jpeg 146w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXtLZL1UMAE_yNu-497x1024.jpeg 497w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXtLZL1UMAE_yNu-768x1582.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXtLZL1UMAE_yNu-746x1536.jpeg 746w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>这两则案例也显示出与习近平相关读音的文字组合及拼音字母也已被纳入敏感词监控范畴。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"crfxTUSlGe\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e5%90%8e%e4%b8%bb/\">【敏感词库】后主</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【敏感词库】后主》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e5%90%8e%e4%b8%bb/embed/#?secret=crfxTUSlGe\" data-secret=\"crfxTUSlGe\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"u7hEvwIRFs\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e7%bf%a0%e4%b8%8e%e7%a5%88%e7%bf%a0%e8%b6%85%e8%af%9d/\">【敏感词库】“翠”与“祈翠超话”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【敏感词库】“翠”与“祈翠超话”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e7%bf%a0%e4%b8%8e%e7%a5%88%e7%bf%a0%e8%b6%85%e8%af%9d/embed/#?secret=u7hEvwIRFs\" data-secret=\"u7hEvwIRFs\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38827,38912,16848],"tags":[40441,13222,40442,9283,19622,40440,40099]}